ast.name: Full Music Player
ast.comment:
This is about as close as I could get to a full featured music player without being able to edit playlists or skip foward/back within a song.
- Browse artists
- Album art included wherever applicable.
- While choosing from an artist's albums, the background is filled with a picture of the band that gets desaturated and colorized (Caching allows the next load time to be much quicker) (Wifi only)
- A time bar is displayed while song plays.
- Share current song to social network.
- Shuffle / repeat
- Shake to randomize song.
- Option to load most recent playlist after re-launching the player.

body.text: Set the screen's background to the album cover.
